These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, december, january, august
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, pakistani, egyptian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
City: prague, nizza, paris, new-york
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the person traveling to prague is not to the left of the person traveling to prague##8
 3. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the person traveling to prague is not to the right of the person traveling to prague##8
 6. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 8. the japanese is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the person traveling to new-york is the egyptian##1
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
12. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
13. the egyptian is not to the left of the person traveling to new-york##8
14. the person who's birthday is in december is the person traveling to paris##1
15. the person who's birthday is in december is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday         | march     | december   | august | january |
| Nationality   | pakistani | japanese   | malaysian   | egyptian  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| City     | prague    | paris | nizza     | new-york    |

