.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, fishing, camping
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, havana, cain, baccarat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, tennis, biathlon, lacrosse
 1. the cain-smoker is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the havana-smoker##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the havana-smoker##8
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4
 9. the swisher-smoker is the person who's sport is tennis##1
10. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the cain-smoker##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
14. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
18. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Hobby          | camping     | board-games | baking | fishing  |
| Cigar   | havana    | cain  | baccarat | swisher |
| Sport           | biathlon | lacrosse | weightlifting    | tennis  |

