.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up, almond-milk, soy-milk
4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, poker, canasta
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, azure, black, amber
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person who likes green##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
 7. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person who likes azure##8
12. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | juice    | soy-milk   | almond-milk | 7up |
| Game   | billiard     | poker  | canasta   | monopoly      |
| Color   | azure | green    | black      | amber       |
| Sport         | sailing    | climbing | surfing   | cycling    |

