 4. the person drinking sprite is between the dancer and the electrician##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
 6. the fan of gospel is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the software-developer##1
10. the electrician is the fan of gospel##1
11. the fan of disco is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
12. the dancer is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
13. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
14. the electrician is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
15. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4

