 4. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
 6. the person who likes brown is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 7. the person who likes mauve is not to the left of the chef##8
 8. the person playing go is the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the person playing domino is not to the left of the doctor##8
10. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
11. the person who likes ivory is between the doctor and the person watching drama movies##2
12. the electrician is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
13. the person playing go is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
14. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
