 3. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the fan of techno##8
 4. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the fan of techno##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the fan of reggae is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
 7. the fan of jazz is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the fan of jazz##7
 9. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5
10. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
11. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
12. the person traveling to liverpool is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
13. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
14. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
