10. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the pakistani##8
11. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
12. the mechanic is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
14. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
