 5. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
 6. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking milk##7
 7. the fan of dubstep is not to the left of the fan of disco##8
 8. the fan of folk is somewhere between the person who likes apricot and the person who likes lilac##7
 9. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who growslily is not to the left of the person who growslily##8
11. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
12. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
13. the fan of dubstep is the person who likes apricot##1
