.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, hamster, horse
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, purple, grey, apricot
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, mexican, nigerian, argentine
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person who likes apricot##1
 2. the mexican is on the right of the argentine##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the polish is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 6. the nigerian is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the mexican is not to the right of the person who likes purple##8
 9. the polish is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
11. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the argentine is in an odd position##4
13. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Pet   | rabbit  | horse      | hamster     | frog     |
| Color         | turquise | grey  | apricot     | purple  |
| Nationality     | polish     | nigerian | argentine | mexican     |

