 4. the owner of the bird is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person playing go is not the owner of the lizard##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the owner of the lizard##8
 8. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person playing go is between the owner of the lizard and the person playing scrabble##2
13. the person playing scrabble is on the far left or far right##3

